(32188, 93230, 0, 2, 'My Little Satellite', '', '2011-01-29 00:00:00', 2011, 0, 1, 4, 'Down the street lies the morning winter breeze. Said you "Aren''t we going outside? Chasing in the sunlight. Sing a sunshine lullaby". You are such a pretty little thing, raised up just below the moonlight, passed through so many times, and we met along the riverside.\r\n\r\nYou are my little satellite. Surrounding me like a fire, just below the rainbow, and make me a better man. I say, even when the world comes to its moribund end, you''ll still be mine, my little satellite.\r\n\r\nWhen winter ends and spring comes in March, said you " Aren''t we going outside? Walking along the riverbank. Drink a sweet hot chocolate". Then I''ll take you to a winding grassland, smell the fresh of the earth, and sing you a song about raindrop serenade.', '', 297, '', 'Nico', 'Nico', 'NICOLE & THE JOEs', 'Riverbank Cowhead Co. Ltd.', '', 0, 0, 0, '2011-01-28 23:43:11', '2015-03-12 13:45:42', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(32189, 93230, 0, 3, '在這個殘破的天空下，如果有一件事情是重要的。', '', '2011-01-29 00:00:00', 2011, 0, 1, 7, '坐上最後一班火車，向南，往太麻里的路上。等待天邊那束日光，在東，灑下炫目的金黃。靈魂靠近灰色海岸，右邊，寧靜無人的七星潭。等待何許人的到來，面前，寫著深沉的詩歌。\r\n\r\n我一個人走路，一個人唱著給妳的歌。一個人剪短了頭髮，在世界的盡頭想妳。\r\n\r\n我說，如果有一件事情是重要的。那一定是和妳一起看星星，看到天空都亮了。然後，緩緩從草原上起身回家。如果，有一件事情是重要的，那決不是虛度浪費生命，直到靈魂都死了。然後，槁木死灰地活著，失去重量。', '', 380, '', 'Nico', 'Nico', 'NICOLE & THE JOEs', 'Riverbank Cowhead Co. Ltd.', '', 0, 0, 0, '2011-01-28 23:48:55', '2015-03-12 13:45:42', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
